{"tid":2169206,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"精神科醫生：記者覆診甩底","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T10:22:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcf6d7166b88a4dbe7c997fcf7f2d62c299407a","tid":2169206,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:07:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/P4RTMTGFDZGNJLXINBVVBNFJHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FP4RTMTGFDZGNJLXINBVVBNFJHY%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6WLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=37ad6b4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FP4RTMTGFDZGNJLXINBVVBNFJHY%2F&h=ae5adec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/P4RTMTGFDZGNJLXINBVVBNFJHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n精神科醫生：記者覆診甩底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2JLHeyg8j21i8yFzda-6j8E5ICk=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2FMAZPTVZ5B6BAGNKWLG7WC7R4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2JLHeyg8j21i8yFzda-6j8E5ICk%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2FMAZPTVZ5B6BAGNKWLG7WC7R4.jpg&h=c20b9509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃以謙<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】事主X案發後被診斷患上適應障礙，帶有抑鬱心境，否認誇大病情。為他診治的精神科醫生黃以謙昨出庭作供，他否認不會質疑病人所說並假設屬實，亦不同意適應障礙是精神病中最輕微類別，指病人或引起自殺念頭。他承認，X曾失約沒應診，聲稱X只是間中服藥，對服藥指示遵守得不算很好。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《東方》及事主17度投訴律政司延誤檢控  辯方：X用盡言詞砌黎智英<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主被辱罵後仍工作兩小時<br />\n<br />\nX於2017年6月至8月曾會見黃以謙三次。黃供稱，X起初稱遭一位名人辱罵，但沒透露身份，X自言憂慮和恐懼，並且失眠，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方問8月24日最後會面時，X是否已完全康復，黃以謙指根據記錄並非如此，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方問黃是否不會質疑病人所說，並假設屬實。黃否認，稱會衡量病人說。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又問，適應障礙是否精神病中最輕微類別，黃不同意，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nX供稱沒向黃誇大病情，只是真實反映。辯方指他沒跟指示服藥「費事食」，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c5efc40d993d469f435885109ea6629264087ef3","tid":2169206,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"要強制佢入青山"},{"pid":"2543b6d9d9bc73408a67d2c953726508022528d1","tid":2169206,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"個阿姑喺狗面前拎刀隊人都有得保釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}